{"tid":409766,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳智思拒評「殺無赦」論","createTime":"2017-09-22T10:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T15:27:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de0a9b711213e0de72c439306e7684bb5223adcd","tid":409766,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:46:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20160526&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20160526%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170922&d=CQ6U9pJmG1NypnZ2%2BLCg%2BYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=b77b82e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20160526%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170922&h=19dc5447\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20160526&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170922</a><br />\n<br />\n陳智思拒評「殺無赦」論<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】繼特首林鄭月娥拒絕評論建制派議員何君堯的「殺無赦」論是否恰當或違法，行政會議召集人陳智思（圖）昨在電台節目上，以中文程度不好、不太理解該番說話為由拒作評論。但他亦指，年輕人不應該因為提倡或談論港獨而受懲罰，社會應思考出現港獨想法的原因。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯上周日在反港獨集會後向傳媒表示，附和對搞港獨者應殺無赦，並發表「呢啲人唔殺咗佢做咩」等言論。本身為泰國華僑的陳智思昨表示，自己不太理解該番話的意思；但他強調太激進的言論，只會令社會日後有更多更激動的言論，對大局而言無好處。<br />\n<br />\n稱大學可討論港獨<br />\n<br />\n至於應否談港獨，陳認為大學有討論港獨的空間，例如探討港獨不可行的原因等，但底線是不能「亂講」或侮辱他人。他又認為，社會不應因年輕人提倡港獨而予以懲罰，應思考年輕人有港獨想法的原因。他指，近年本港在經濟及民生上不斷與內地融合，或令人有「香港已變質」的感覺，亦可以理解年輕人為何會對內地感到抗拒，應正面地向年輕人作出分析，而非完全禁絕港獨的討論空間。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t中大學生會　拆港獨橫額續與校方談判　釐清文化廣場使用規則<br />\n港聞 13小時前"},{"pid":"86fe15f7b69826d02d9d501a36fe2478612971d3","tid":409766,"uid":71596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"咁搵人翻譯英文比佢"},{"pid":"f447f02bb1b64f79058e5aaa17487c0fc2e649be","tid":409766,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"中文唔好點做終國人呀阿陳生"},{"pid":"9bde2677cd736bf27227f4e19468b775d8cb1954","tid":409766,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"死返秦國啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed55d63ead85276279b2a094d1c0cd424bd08ff","tid":409766,"uid":118771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死返秦國啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9999af235b5588eece27d4ac68450436f63817c4","tid":409766,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:27:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">newlife五毛起底</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bzoe9k7q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbzoe9k7q&h=99ae6483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fgzy3w50\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffgzy3w50&h=bf68cf95&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}